{
  "texts": [
    "The above analysis and results demonstrate the fact that virtual learning fosters an interactive process of teaching and learning, in which the teaching and learning practices are much more student-centered and activate students\" engagement and motivation towards complete, virtually digital learning.",
    "This, in turn, serves to reveal the importance of having virtual learning, not only to expand learning opportunities but also to serve as an unavoidable and dependable instrument in the educational process.",
    "The analysis shows that students\" engagement is positively influenced by virtual learning.",
    "The positive impact has been manifested in many potential components constituting the whole concept of engagement.",
    "These include students\" attendance, classroom participation, learning motivation, learning anxiety, students\" self-efficacy, the acquisition of language skills, and students\" willingness to communicate."
  ]
}